extends layout

block content
  if success
    p Thanks for creating a new watcher!
    p You will receive and email whenever new rooms become available that match you criteria.
    p You have also been sent an email that includes a link you can use to cancel the watcher at any time.
    p #[a(href="/") Make another!]
  else
    p Something went terribly wrong! #[a(href="/") Start over :(]
